181
00:27:17,403 --> 00:27:20,698
These are some ripe petunias.

182
00:27:20,782 --> 00:27:22,659
Hold this, please.

183
00:27:30,416 --> 00:27:32,210
Want it?

184
00:27:34,379 --> 00:27:37,966
- Getting anything on this?
- Not a bleep.

185
00:27:38,049 --> 00:27:39,717
All right.

186
00:27:42,637 --> 00:27:44,222
Give me that.

187
00:27:54,107 --> 00:27:56,734
- I thought it was a car afire.
- It is a car afire.

188
00:27:56,818 --> 00:28:00,280
Wendell said there's something
in the back country too.

189
00:28:00,363 --> 00:28:01,364
Step in there.

190
00:28:01,447 --> 00:28:04,409
When's the county gonna start
paying rent on my horse?

191
00:28:04,492 --> 00:28:07,579
- I love you more and more every day.
- That's very nice.

192
00:28:08,955 --> 00:28:10,582
- Be careful.
- Always am.

193
00:28:10,665 --> 00:28:12,375
- Don't get hurt.
- Never do.

194
00:28:12,458 --> 00:28:14,294
Don't hurt no one.

195
00:28:16,588 --> 00:28:18,423
If you say so.

196
00:28:52,666 --> 00:28:56,462
- Wouldn't think a car'd burn like that.
- Yes, sir.

197
00:28:57,171 --> 00:28:58,881
We should've brought wienies.

198
00:28:58,964 --> 00:29:01,884
That look like about
a '77 Ford to you, Wendell?

199
00:29:01,967 --> 00:29:05,179
- It could be.
- I'd say it is. Not a doubt in my mind.

200
00:29:05,262 --> 00:29:10,267
- The old boy shot by the highway?
- Yes, sir. His vehicle.

201
00:29:10,351 --> 00:29:14,522
Man killed Lamar's deputy, took his car,
killed that man on the highway...

202
00:29:14,605 --> 00:29:20,027
...swapped for his car, now here it is and
he's swapped again for God knows what.

203
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:22,488
That's very linear, sheriff.

204
00:29:23,531 --> 00:29:26,742
- Age'll flatten a man, Wendell.
- Yes, sir.

205
00:29:26,825 --> 00:29:28,911
- Then there's this other.
- Yeah.

206
00:29:30,996 --> 00:29:33,165
- You ride Winston.
- You sure?

207
00:29:33,249 --> 00:29:37,503
Oh, I'm more than sure. If anything
happens to Loretta's horse out here...

208
00:29:37,586 --> 00:29:41,048
I can tell you, I don't want
to be the party that was aboard.

209
00:29:41,131 --> 00:29:46,011
