217
00:30:13,289 --> 00:30:16,041
Oh, hell's bells,
they even shot the dog.

218
00:30:19,003 --> 00:30:21,297
This is just
a deal gone wrong, isn't it?

219
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:25,634
Yup. Appears to have been
a glitch or two.

220
00:30:29,263 --> 00:30:33,185
